{"tid":405101,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"點解當年超任博士可以公然賣,仲賣廣告?","createTime":"2017-09-18T14:51:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T01:24:22.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"41aebde0172e8e6f3ecedfbb35fa1f743864395f","tid":405101,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:51:31.000Z","msg":"其實過左千禧年,我估好多老屎忽都出來做野,為生活搵食,最後一次沉迷打機既多數係ps2,ps2我無打過,nds psp wii更加係機都未掂過,唔想只係活在人地設計既遊戲世界裡面 <br />\n<br />\n望番呢兩年既香港,都唔識點形容,我都唔想只係懷念過去點好,香港....,.唉,保重各位當年玩過超任的巴打"},{"pid":"ca050089db42745721790e68da189b1c7601d5da","tid":405101,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:51:46.000Z","msg":"當年黃金有啲舖好仆街 <br />\n抄碟已經貴過好多地方 <br />\n新game出抄碟再要貴啲 <br />\n返屋企附近抄返統一價條氣順啲"},{"pid":"1e959d63cc2c63497721e7ed02371e461ccc07a1","tid":405101,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:52:04.000Z","msg":"當年copy碟既鋪頭真係做到發達買數 <br />\n鋪租已經平，每日一車車學生放學十蚊廿蚊俾佢地"},{"pid":"9a1c4dc662839b7363cdf721c190acff7b77399d","tid":405101,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:52:15.000Z","msg":"以前康怡有一間，$5抄一隻floppy。以前每個星期都大拿拿用$50抄game。 <br />\n佢有個list，寫低no.之後抄比你。 <br />\n記得之前有隻game話美少女，諗住同sailor moon有關啦！Load完之後一開係著住三點式既卡通人物，俾阿媽鬧到飛起。"},{"pid":"5f8c8b8bfe3201eb8e414ac723f2e824bb0ff488","tid":405101,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:52:47.000Z","msg":"成個超任年代只係買過一隻快手旋風插係機頂 <br />\n真係,GAME廠可以話食屎 <br />\n個時GAME鋪係有條LIST,你買佢就即時錄碟比你 <br />\n好記得一眼見到太空戰士6!,即買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://modacooltey.myweb.hinet.net/data_save/hero3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmodacooltey.myweb.hinet.net%2Fdata_save%2Fhero3.gif&h=01a2c4b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三國志3係玩得最長時間既一集,後尾個D都冇乜點玩了<br />\n第一次係在野搜到趙雲真係驚為天人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n超任個時真係盛世<br />\n講起都懷念"},{"pid":"afdfbc9ca04a97f08aa6962c051a1c1d41282560","tid":405101,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:53:22.000Z","msg":"時代唔同。 <br />\n現在都唔流行買斷隻game <br />\n一係dlc , 唔係就免費下載再課金 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩得ps4，都上番一定年經，至少唔會小學雞，都唔介意花幾舊買game，好過花成日去搵破解，出來做野你先會覺得打機先係窮人玩兒，對比以前睇人花幾百買game覺得很豪，現在睇番買車買樓玩音響，真係覺得以前小學雞"},{"pid":"00d55041ca4399ffc7d1d72317520691269b018d","tid":405101,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:53:58.000Z","msg":"其實你話16001無記錯係STREET FIGHTER 2 <br />\n大約係1992-3年個時 <br />\n上網仲要靠MODERN <br />\nBBS先岩岩係港台興起運行緊 <br />\n一般學生根本無乜能力可以自己係網上DOWNLOAD隻SFC GAME抄出黎玩 <br />\n而個時仲係SFC大紅時期 <br />\n基本上所有Game都係由兩三個要收錢隱蔽度幾高嘅bbs群發佈 <br />\n而呢幾個group入面有一個我知道由8x年代尾已經係度賣緊fc game"},{"pid":"576a9f752b0b132e5b25cb18e6f7ef6f14b59685","tid":405101,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T17:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664e2015e02d3ffb33cbfb14cd9de24004af8349","tid":405101,"uid":84,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T06:34:22.000Z","msg":"細個同屋企人打機係最開心嘅回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"250c628ec600b9cc25e4cc484faf661f818f1675","tid":405101,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:56:43.000Z","msg":"其實超任博士玩唔玩到要用到Super FX或SA1呢兩粒附加晶片的game? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f893b25f442f50cd96664e16f6837b963e3c6807","tid":405101,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T12:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d6a4cf31bc0cd6ee22ac43a842c663f1aa63c2","tid":405101,"uid":575