"pid":"b17ba343fd66f50bb19029169ab6086696e13b80","tid":405101,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T08:59:52.000Z","msg":"16160 幽遊白書-特別篇"},{"pid":"c3b6f2650dd6830417e46325474418708d533596","tid":405101,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:07:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實超任博士玩唔玩到要用到Super FX或SA1呢兩粒附加晶片的game? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要買其中一隻game插落去就玩得。<br />\n<br />\n記得當時係sale改game而唔係sale老翻。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢個廣告都係講慢動作 無限復活, 無講老翻<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L-RtsxvGyHQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DL-RtsxvGyHQ&d=UzWHiFDZ68nYT9RT6v2vLwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=aa859c0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L-RtsxvGyHQ</a>"},{"pid":"3a8ca27bcf2b8e2470fc7db069d07259b2f44d10","tid":405101,"uid":48623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:09:14.000Z","msg":"我當年算係早個批玩超任博士，好記得部博士係第三代，16M，要玩 16M 以上既 Game 要加 Ram，而個時亦都唔算多 Game 係 16M 以上，係去到中期既聖劍傳說、機戰四先用得著，個時成四五舊水。<br />\n但好彩既係個時表哥教左我點 Copy D Game 落隻新 Floppy 到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n咁我就做左個級入面既二手老翻專家，同學仔夾錢比我去荃豐買 Game，我自己就買吉碟再 Copy 比佢地，個時無記錯 D Game 係用 Floppy 計，五蚊一隻 Floppy。咁我就收佢地三蚊一隻 Floppy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n努力左大半年之後就夠錢買 Ram 再發大來做。好記得機戰同聖劍傳說個期放假基本上係 Copy Game。<br />\n到後來直情夠我買部 PS 添 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cdd10523b31f1fcfa4bf27df3d2f39560458ade","tid":405101,"uid":137248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"呢個post應該全部都係三十歲以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c477d61f382b857f6190e92bca7060fa4799eb0","tid":405101,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:54:04